Some sample options are not supported under defaults.
This is flagged during config validation.

  $ cat >config.yaml <<~~
  > defaults:
  >   min_date: 2016
  >   group_by: year
  > samples:
  >   focal:
  >     query: region == 'North America'
  >     min_date: 2016-05-01
